our analysis. The analysis of a single quantum\nswitch that creates multipartite entanglements for different sets of users is a\nspecial case of our work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2021 22:19:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-03"}
