00% using a\ndual-flowmeter. Consisting of a traditional 22mm breathing circuit, a\nnon-vented CPAP mask, and a Positive End-Expiratory Pressure (PEEP) valve, the\nCPAP can provide positive pressures between 5-20 cm H2O. The device is\nmanufactured using local 3D printing and workshop facilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jun 2021 06:55:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-03"}
