\\sim$ 0.6 % in this\nlow velocity wind could correspond to an abundance of $\\sim$ 0.9 % at 1 au.\nFinally, as the two streams roughly correspond to the spatial extent of a\nswitchback patch, we suggest that patches are distinct features of coronal hole\nwind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jun 2021 11:11:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-10"}
