t of\nthe applicability of existing optimization methods to the defined problem is\nmade, including metaheuristics/EA and Deep Learning methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jun 2021 14:26:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 23:09:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2022 09:15:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-22"}
